n%20Assam.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F5jrrcslg_bhutan-gelephu-mindfulness-city_625x300_30_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'MINDFULNESS%20CITY'%20-%20BUT%20WHY%20IN%20GELEPHU%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20in%20Gelephu%20is%20%26quot%3Bbeautiful%20and%20pristine%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20the%20Butanese%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20region%20is%20a%20biological%20hot%20spot%2C%20with%20abundant%20potential%20for%20clean%20energy%2C%20but%20why%20this%20mega%20project%20here%3F%20he%20had%20asked%20the%20King%2C%20wondering%20why%20such%20a%20project%20was%20not%20being%20considered%20for%20Thimphu%20or%20Paro%20-%20where%20there%20is%20ready%20infrastructure%2C%20like%20airports%2C%20highways%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fdlmm697s_bhutan-gelephu-mindfulness-city_625x300_30_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20King%20had%20a%20one-word%20reply%20for%20the%20prime%20minister%20-%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B.%20He%20then%20explained%20that%20%26quot%3BOur%20future%20is%20linked%20with%20India.%20If%20we%20chose%20any%20other%20place%2C%20then%20such%20a%20project%20may%20succeed%2C%20it%20may%20have%20its%20challenges%2C%20but%20if%20we%20plan%20this%20along%20the%20border%20with%20India%2C%20the%20concept%20itself%20will%20drive%20it%20to%20success%2C%20because%20Bhutan's%20future%20is%20intrinsically%20linked%20with%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prime%20minister%20recalled%20the%20King%20having%20said%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Foaompv6s_bhutan-gelephu-mindfulness-city_625x300_30_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20finally%20understood%20the%20strategic%20significance%20of%20the%20project%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Gelephu%20Mindfulness%20City%20is%20not%20about%20Bhutan%20-%20it%20is%20about%20Bhutan%20and%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDETAILS%20ABOUT%20THE%20CITY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20built%2C%20Bhutan's%20'Mindfulness%20City'%20will%20cover%20nearly%202.5%25%20of%20the%20entire%20country's%20landmass%20and%20will%20be%20bigger%20than%20all%20of%20Singapore.%20A%20more%20local%20comparison%20will%20be%20to%20Bhutan's%20capital%20city%2C%20Thimphu.%20While%20Gelephu%20City%20will%20be%20more%20than%202%2C500%20square%20kilometers%2C%20capital%20city%20Thimphu%20is%20just%2026%20square%20kilometers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fpkkh82n_bhutan-gelephu-mindfulness-city_625x300_30_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20will%20be%20built%20around%20a%20series%20of%20inhabitable%20bridges.%20It%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20low-rise%20city%20which%20will%20have%20its%20own%20university%2C%20health%20care%20facilities%20for%20both%20western%20and%20traditional%20medicine.%20It%20will%20also%20have%20several%20markets%20and%20spiritual%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fc8j1jdq8_bhutan-gelephu-mindfulness-city_625x300_30_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20plans%20to%20build%20a%20hydroelectric%20power%20project%20and%20a%20hydroponic%20greenhouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20spread%20over%2011%20major%20neighbourhoods%20which%20will%20span%20across%20the%20region's%20thirty-five%20rivers%20and%20streams.%20The%20city%20design%20and%20planning%20is%20done%20such%20that%20neighbourhoods%20will%20be%20like%20mandalas%2C%20with%20public%20spaces%20towards%20the%20city%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fct2pf5ms_bhutan-gelephu-mindfulness-city_625x300_30_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20will%20be%20entirely%20based%20on%20Bhutan's%20Gross%20National%20Happiness%20philosophy%20which%20has%20been%20praised%20the%20world%20over.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20project%2C%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Bhutan%20had%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BMindfulness%20City%20will%20be%20unique%20as%20it%20would%20not%20just%20prioritise%20economic%20development%2C%20but%20will%20focus%20on%20personal%20well-being%20of%20every%20resident.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Photo%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F4gertf8o_bhutan-gelephu-mindfulness-city_625x300_30_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20big.dk%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20will%20have%20its%20own%20international%20airport%20-%20construction%20for%20which%20has%20already%20begin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gelephu%20'Mindfullness%20City'%20rethinks%20how%20the%20cities%20of%2