.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-demands-resignation-of-un-expert-francesca-albanese-over-genocidal-campaign-against-palestinians-remark%2Famp_articleshow%2F114799057.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump's%20Net%20Worth%20Doubled%20In%20October%20To%20%248%20Billion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20net%20worth%20has%20grown%20exponentially%20this%20month%2C%20increasing%20from%20under%20%244%20billion%20at%20the%20start%20of%20October%20to%20%248%20billion%20Tuesday.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E'%20real-time%20billionaires%20tracker%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20is%20now%20the%20357th-wealthiest%20person%20in%20the%20world.%20His%20fortune%20swelled%20as%20his%20social%20media%20company's%20shares%20reached%20their%20highest%20level%20since%20June%205.%20Trump%20Media%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%20Group%20closed%20up%20nearly%209%25%20on%20Tuesday%20at%20%2451.51.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20Media's%20share%20increase%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20linked%20to%20the%20company's%20financial%20performance%3B%20instead%2C%20it%20has%20moved%20with%20the%20odds%20of%20Mr%20Trump%20winning%20the%20election%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fantoniopequenoiv%2F2024%2F10%2F29%2Fdonald-trumps-net-worth-has-doubled-in-october-to-8-billion-as-trump-media-stock-skyrockets%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20most%20polls%20find%20the%20Republican%20leader%20and%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20virtually%20tied%20across%20the%20seven%20battleground%20states%20expected%20to%20determine%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20election%2C%20and%20major%20election%20forecasts%20suggest%20the%20race%20is%20a%20tossup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ECNN%20%3C%2Fem%3Epoll%2C%20in%20Arizona%2C%20Ms%20Harris%20has%2048%25%20support%20among%20likely%20voters%2C%20while%20Trump%20has%2047%25.%20In%20Nevada%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20leads%20slightly%20with%2048%25%2C%20compared%20to%2047%25%20%C2%A0for%20Ms%20Harris.%20These%20narrow%20margins%20are%20within%20the%20poll's%20margin%20of%20error%2C%20indicating%20no%20clear%20frontrunner%20in%20either%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20latest%20presidential%20forecast%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hill%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Mr%20Trump%20bests%20Ms%20Harris%20with%20the%20former%20having%2054%25%20support%20and%20the%20latter%2046%25.%20The%20former%20President%20holds%20a%20narrow%20lead%20in%20five%20of%20six%20swing%20states%20-%20Nevada%2C%20Arizona%2C%20Georgia%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20and%20Wisconsin%20-%20while%20Ms%20Harris%20has%20a%20slight%20edge%20in%20Michigan.%20However%2C%20the%20gap%20remains%20within%20the%20typical%20polling%20error%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hill.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20national%20polls%20are%20a%20useful%20guide%20as%20to%20how%20popular%20a%20candidate%20is%20across%20the%20whole%20country%2C%20they're%20not%20the%20best%20way%20to%20predict%20the%20election%20result.%20Polls%20are%20just%20designed%20to%20broadly%20explain%20how%20the%20public%20feels%20about%20a%20candidate%20or%20an%20issue%2C%20not%20predict%20the%20result%20of%20an%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-presidential-elections-arnold-schwarzenegger-endorses-kamala-harris-slams-donald-trumps-trash-can-comment-6910677%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20Am%20An%20American%20Before%20A%20Republican%26quot%3B%3A%20Arnold%20Schwarzenegger%20Endorses%20Kamala%20Harris%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Kamala%20Harris'%20net%20worth%2C%20along%20with%20her%20husband%20Doug%20Emhoff%2C%20currently%20stands%20at%20%248%20million%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EForbes%20%3C%2Fem%3Eestimates%20published%20in%20May%20this%20year.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20roughly%2020%20times%20the%20median%20net%20