d-hamas-massacre-warned-against-overreliance-on-air-force%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaptly%20summed%20up%20this%20view%20in%202018%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20arguing%20Israel%20needed%20an%20%26quot%3Balternative%20to%20the%20air%20force%26quot%3B%20and%20couldn't%20%26quot%3Bafford%20to%20put%20all%20our%20eggs%20into%20one%20basket%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20sophisticated%20that%20basket%20may%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Israeli%20Air%20Force's%20use%20of%20various%20ALBMs%20suggests%20some%20middle%20ground%20was%20ultimately%20reached.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BNow%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20the%20IDF%20adopted%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20long-range%20missile%20system%20with%20conventional%20warheads%20%E2%80%94%20but%20instead%20of%20establishing%20a%20separate%20missile%20corps%2C%20it%20mounted%20these%20missiles%20on%20the%20attack%20aircraft%20that%20will%20serve%20as%20flying%20launchpads%2C%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2Fsecurity-aviation%2F2024-10-23%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Fas-israel-readies-to-strike-iran-the-pentagon-spills-its-allys-secrets-in-real-time%2F00000192-b587-d40d-abb3-ff9772fd0000%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enoted%20a%20recent%20article%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20Israeli%20newspaper%20Haaretz.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20air%20force%20vanquished%20all%20its%20critics%20and%20rivals%20and%20clearly%20maintained%20its%20primacy%20in%20the%20IDF.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Israel%20does%20have%20an%20arsenal%20of%20land-based%20Jericho%20intermediate-range%20ballistic%20missiles%20(IRBMs)%2C%20these%20are%20reserved%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-hezbollah-israel-hidden-nuclear-weapons-arsenal-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enu