%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fapple-vision-pro-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20Vision%20Pro%3C%2Fa%3E%20extensively%20and%20tried%20several%20other%20VR%20devices%20over%20the%20years.%20This%20made%20me%20curious%20to%20see%20how%20the%20Quest%203S%20performs.%20With%20its%20reasonable%20price%20and%20solid%20specifications%2C%20could%20this%20be%20the%20ideal%20gateway%20device%20for%20newcomers%20looking%20to%20enter%20the%20world%20of%20VR%20gaming%20and%20media%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20time%20immersed%20in%20the%203S%2C%20I%20can%20confidently%20say%20that%20it's%20a%20great%20on-ramp%20for%20anyone%20ready%20to%20dip%20their%20toes%20into%20VR%20tech.%20It's%20not%20quite%20as%20good%20as%20the%20flagship%20Quest%203%20but%20it's%20not%20that%20far%20off.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Quest%203S%20is%20the%20best%20overall%20value%20in%20the%20VR%20space%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22533b5142-5661-4a89-b057-ebf4645345a0%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Performance%20and%20design%5C%22%3EThe%20Quest%203S%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20a%20budget%20VR%20headset%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20wearing%20a%20Meta%20Quest%203S%20VR%20headset.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67224d6801ea6d83dee51253%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDespite%20its%20lower%20price%2C%20the%20Quest%203S%20uses%20the%20same%20processor%20as%20the%20flagship%20Quest%203.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20still%20sells%20the%20more%20expensive%20Quest%203%2C%20released%20in%202023%2C%20which%20remains%20the%20brand's%20flagship%20model.%20This%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20look%20at%20the%20cheaper%20Quest%203S%20as%20a%20budget%20VR%20device.%20But%20any%20concerns%20about%20subpar%20performance%20were%20immediately%20dismissed%20the%20second%20I%20strapped%20this%20headset%20to%20my%20face.%20It%20fits%20a%20bit%20differently%20than%20the%20Quest%203%2C%20but%20nothing%20about%20the%203S%20feels%20cheap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20that%20point%2C%20the%203S%20uses%20the%20same%20Qualcomm%20Snapdragon%20XR2%20Gen%202%20chipset%20with%208GB%20of%20RAM%20as%20the%20Quest%203.%20The%20headset%20isn't%20a%20lesser%20product%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20raw%20processing%20power.%20And%20like%20the%20Quest%203%2C%20the%203S%20comes%20with%20the%20same%20two%20wireless%20controllers%20for%20tracking%20input.%20I%20found%20them%20comfortable%20to%20hold%20and%20responsive.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20opt%20to%20turn%20on%20hand-tracking%20to%20physically%20pinch%20at%20virtual%20menus%20with%20your%20fingers%20instead%20of%20pressing%20the%20controller's%20buttons.%20Despite%20needing%20to%20change%20their%20AA%20batteries%20every%20few%20months%2C%20I%20prefer%20using%20the%20controllers%20over%20hand-tracking.%20They're%20a%20much%20better%20experience%20for%20navigating%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person's%20hand%20holding%20a%20Meta%20Quest%203S%20VR%20controller.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672256d49b3250dbbceb21da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Quest%203S%20and%20Quest%203%20use%20the%20same%20wireless%20controllers.%20%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20looking%20to%20upgrade%20from%20an%20older%20Quest%202%2C%20Meta%20says%20this%20new%20device%20has%20twice%20the%20graphics%20(GPU)%20performance%20as%20that%20model%2C%20which%20sported%20an%20XR2%20Gen%201%20chipset.%20The%20speed%20bump%20is%20noticeable%2C%20but%20the%20jump%20in%20passthrough%20quality%20is%20an%20even%20bigger%20reason%20to%20upgrade.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVR%20passthrough%20is%20a%20feature%20that%20uses%20the%20headset's%20cameras%20to%20let%20you%20see%20your%20surroundings%20in%20real%20time.%20Passthrough%20was%20also%20supported%20on%20the%20Quest%202%2C%20but%20that%20headset's%20black-and-white%20implementation%20was%20lacking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20there's%20no%20more%20grainy%20grayscale%20video%20of%20the%20world%20around%20you.%20Instead%2C%20Meta%20cites%20a%204.5-time%20improvement%20in%20camera%20resolution%20and%20the%20switch%20to%20color%20presents%20a%20nearly%20night-and-day%20difference.%20This%20step%20forward%20in%20passthrough%20enables%20better%20mixed-reality%20experiences%20where%20overlayed%20virtual%20objects%20can%20interact%20with%20your%20physical%20space.%20For%20example%2C%20an%20alien%20can%20appear%20to%20burst%20through%20your%20bedroom%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20step-up%20Quest%203%20headset%20also%20has%20full-color%20passthrough%20support%2C%20and%20it%20looks%20a%20bit%20sharper%2C%20but%20the%203S%20is%20no%20slouch.%20The%20option%20to%20get%20such%20solid%20mixed-reality%20quality%20on%20a%20headset%20this%20affordable%20is%20a%20big%20deal.%20Although%20it's%20great%20to%20be%20fully%20immersed%20in%20certain%20games%2C%20there%20are%20times%20when%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20completely%20shut%20out%20from%20your%20surroundings.%20Better%20yet%2C%20some%20apps%20like%20PianoVision%20use%20mixed%20reality%20to%20teach%20new%20skills.%20That%20title%20can%20overlay%20notes%20on%20top%20of%20an%20actual%20piano%20to%20help%20people%20learn%20to%20play%20new%20songs%20%E2%80%94%20think%20Guitar%20Hero%20but%20for%20the%20piano%20in%20your%20living%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20view%20of%20a%20Meta%20Quest%203S%20headset%20resting%20on%20a%20table%20in%20front%20of%20a%20plant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67225675a0a0cc14f224f4fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20headset's%20elastic%20strap%20isn't%20the%20easiest%20to%20adjust%20so%20you%20might%20want%20to%20upgrade%20to%20a%20third-party%20option.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you're%20fully%20immersed%20or%20using%20mixed%20reality%2C%20the%20Quest%203S%20has%20an%20average%20battery%20life%20of%202.5%20hours.%20That%20might%20sound%20low%2C%20but%20it's%20actually%20a%20little%20longer%20than%20the%20flagship%20Quest%203%2C%20which%20is%20rated%20for%202.2%20hours.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20I%20never%20needed%20the%20headset%20to%20last%20longer%20than%20its%20battery%20allowed.%20Two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20is%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20time%20to%20stay%20focused%20on%20a%20screen.%20In%20the%20same%20way%20you%20might%20need%20to%20put%20your%20smartphone%20down%20after%20using%20it%20for%20a%20while%2C%20it's%20beneficial%20to%20take%20breaks%20with%20VR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20headset%20isn't%20heavy%20by%20most%20standards.%20Its%20514-gram%20weight%20is%20just%20slightly%20less%20than%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20Quest%203%20(though%20the%20Quest%203%20is%20actually%20more%20compact%20in%20appearance).%20However%2C%20I'm%20not%20crazy%20about%20the%20default%20elastic%20strap%20that%20comes%20in%20the%20box.%20I%20find%20it%20hard%20to%20adjust%20to%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20alleviate%20this%20issue%2C%20I%20use%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-74124-20%26h%3D4c53b28f6c3c14b88155eb0b5c3859fad52bfa20a2d13c379cf82b536bb0f091%26postID%3D67211a9e3a35c2732d4551e1%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fmeta-quest-3s-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FKIWI-design-Comfort-Strap-Compatible%252Fdp%252FB0CMW2WTNJ%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethird-party%20strap%3C%2Fa%3E%20similar%20to%20Meta's%20Quest%20Elite%20Strap%2C%20which%20offloads%20more%20pressure%20to%20the