that's%20worth%20considering%20to%20access%20a%20rotating%20catalog%20of%20titles%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20Quest%203S%20is%20a%20very%20capable%20gaming%20and%20digital%20entertainment%20device%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20it%20can't%20compete%20with%20something%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-74124-20%26h%3Dd75023478f6e99ff62278b733848177bc3eb046a0fc9345a9370589308cf15df%26postID%3D67211a9e3a35c2732d4551e1%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fmeta-quest-3s-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.apple.com%252Fshop%252Fbuy-vision%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20Vision%20Pro%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20high-end%20spatial%20computer.%20There%20is%20remote%20desktop%20support%2C%20but%20the%20experience%20isn't%20on%20the%20same%20level%20as%20Apple's%20device.%20If%20you're%20willing%20to%20spend%20%243%2C500%20on%20a%20headset%20that%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20virtual%20laptop%2C%20then%20you%20should%20consider%20the%20Vision%20Pro%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22733e9a06-7511-44e8-b266-5fb8222c2527%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Comparison%20to%20Quest%203%5C%22%3EThe%203S%20compares%20favorably%20to%20the%20Quest%203%2C%20but%20its%20display%20isn't%20as%20sharp%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222913%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Meta%20Quest%203%20(left)%20next%20to%20the%20Meta%20Quest%203S%20(right).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672256b39b3250dbbceb2174%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221942%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Meta%20Quest%203%20(left)%20has%20a%20thinner%20design%20than%20the%20Meta%20Quest%203S%20(right).%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Meta's%20VR%20headset%20lineup%2C%20the%20Quest%203S%20sits%20a%20step%20below%20the%20Quest%203%20and%20a%20step%20above%20the%20discontinued%20Quest%202.%20In%20that%20context%2C%20the%20new%20headset%20is%20a%20worthy%20upgrade%20for%20people%20who%20still%20have%20a%20Quest%202.%20What's%20more%20interesting%2C%20however%2C%20is%20how%20well%20it%20compares%20to%20the%20more%20expensive%20Quest%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20advantage%20of%20the%20pricier%20Quest%203%20is%20its%20superior%20display.%20Inside%2C%20you%20get%20a%20resolution%20of%202%2C064%20x%202%2C208%20instead%20of%201%2C832%20x%201%2C920%20on%20the%203S.%20The%20Quest%203%20also%20delivers%20more%20pixels%20per%20inch%2C%201%2C218%20versus%20773%2C%20and%20more%20pixels%20per%20degree%2C%2025%20compared%20to%2020.%20There's%20a%20110%20horizontal-%20and%2096%20vertical-degree%20field%20of%20view%20on%20the%20Quest%203%2C%20which%20is%20slightly%20larger%20than%20the%2096%20horizontal%20and%2090%20vertical%20views%20you%20get%20on%20the%203S.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20numbers%20that%20may%20not%20mean%20much%20to%20anyone%20who%20hasn't%20put%20on%20a%20VR%20headset%20before.%20In%20practice%2C%20I%20did%20notice%20the%20difference%20in%20screen%20resolution%20and%20display%20technology%2C%20but%20primarily%20because%20I%20was%20comparing%20them%20directly.%20Everything%20was%20crisper%20and%20smoother%20inside%20the%20pricer%20model.%20Discerning%20users%20who%20are%20more%20dedicated%20to%20VR%20will%20want%20the%20Quest%203.%20Even%20the%20field%20of%20view%20is%20noticeable%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20it.%20But%20most%20people%20playing%20casual%20games%20and%20taking%20their%20first%20steps%20in%20VR%20will%20be%20content%20with%20the%203S.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20the%20lenses%20of%20a%20Meta%20Quest%203S%20VR%20headset.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672257b101ea6d83dee518ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Quest%203S%20uses%20fresnel%20lenses%20and%20has%20a%20lower%20resolution%20than%20the%20Quest%203%2C%20which%20has%20pancake%20lenses%20and%20a%20shaper%20image.%20%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20internal%20display%2C%20I%20noticed%20the%20physical%20size%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20headsets%20more%20than%20I%20thought%20I%20would.%20The%20Quest%203%20uses%20more%20advanced%20pancake%20lens%20technology%20versus%20the%20fresnel%20lens%20tech%20on%20the%203S%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20Quest%203%20is%20thinner.%20I%20found%20the%20face%20cushion%20on%20the%20Quest%203%20to%20be%20slightly%20more%20contoured%20to%20my%20face%20and%20fit%20better%20than%20the%203S.%20The%20size%20and%20shape%20are%20nicer%20on%20the%20more%20expensive%20unit%2C%20but%20not%20different%20enough%20to%20justify%20spending%20an%20extra%20%24200%20for%20that%20aspect%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20things%20considered%2C%20if%20you're%20a%20daily%20VR%20user%20and%20want%20the%20sharpest%20image%2C%20I%20would%20opt%20for%20the%20pricier%20Quest%203.%20If%20VR%20is%20more%20of%20a%20casual%20hobby%20and%20something%20you're%20easing%20into%2C%20the%20cheaper%203S%20is%20the%20better%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224063a44e-ac0d-487d-8bd0-5e21f412e50d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20it%3F%5C%22%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20Meta%20Quest%203S%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Meta%20Quest%203S%20headset%20being%20held%20in%20a%20person's%20hand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672256e201ea6d83dee51811%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeta's%20Quest%203S%20is%20an%20excellent%20VR%20headset%20for%20newcomers%20and%20buyers%20who%20don't%20want%20to%20spend%20top%20dollar%20for%20the%20Quest%203.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption