3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlapan%20Banerjee%2C%20the%20Chief%20Advisor%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20addressed%20the%20media%20on%20this%20issue%20at%20the%20state%20secretariat%2C%20Nabanna%2C%20this%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20allegations%20of%20nepotism%20and%20corruption%2C%20the%20state%20has%20ordered%20re-verification%20of%20housing%20scheme%20beneficiaries.%20For%20this%2C%20the%20secretariat%20has%20issued%20new%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20verify%20data%20to%20reconsider%20the%20names%20omitted%20from%20the%20list%20of%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20there%20was%20tension%20between%20two%20factions%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20South%2024%20Parganas%20district's%20Gosaba-Bali%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20came%20a%20day%20after%20locals%20and%20a%20faction%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20workers%20held%20protests%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%20Development%20Minister%2C%20accusing%20him%20and%20the%20local%20MLA%20of%20corruption%20in%20the%20process%20of%20preparing%20lists%20of%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20housing%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolent%20protests%20erupted%20in%20the%20area%20and%20several%20motorbikes%20were%20torched.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20evening%20Alapan%20Banerjee%20told%20reporters%2C%20%26quot%3BSince%20the%20Central%20government%20is%20not%20giving%20any%20fund%2C%20the%20state%20is%20doing%20the%20survey%20so%20proper%20lists%20can%20be%20given%20to%20the%20centre%20regarding%20housing%20scheme%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20scheme%20under%20which%20the%20Central%20government%20would%20give%2060%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20state%20would%20give%2040%20per%20cent%20but%20since%20the%20Centre%20is%20not%20giving%20anything%2C%20the%20state%20is%20doing%20the%20survey%20so%20that%20the%20state%20can%20provide%20an%20Awas%20Yojana.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20leader%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%20the%20BJP%20is%20trying%20their%20best%20to%20stop%20work.%20They%20want%20to%20punish%20the%20people%20of%20Bengal.%20Seeing%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20working%20for%20the%20poor%20people%20of%20Bengal%2C%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20defame%20her.%20Distribution%20of%20houses%20will%20be%20done%20phase%20wise%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20Opposition%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20retaliated%2C%20alleging%20a%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20list%26quot%3B%20is%20being%20prepared%20by%20the%20state%20government%20%26quot%3Bto%20get%20some%20money%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730313420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Foo3n4mr_bengal-tension_625x300_31_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftension-in-bengal-over-housing-scheme-state-orders-list-verification-6910920%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tension%20erupted%20in%20a%20part%20of%20West%20Bengal's%20South%2024%20Parganas%20district%20over%20lists%20of%20beneficiaries%20in%20the%20state's%20housing%20scheme.%20The%20Trinamool%20Congress%20government%20has%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20build%20new%20homes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Won't%20allow%20'non-Sanatanis'%20to%20set%20up%20shops%20during%20Kumbh%20Mela%2C%20says%20Akhara%20Parishad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730313401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114795193%2Cimgsize-1458477.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fabap-demands-kumbh-land-exclusively-for-sanatanis-amid-controversy%2Farticleshow%2F114789557.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Akhara%20Parishad%20(ABAP)%20has%20declared%20that%20non-Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Jains%2C%20or%20Buddhists%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20to