ted%20lakhs%20of%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%20his%20scathing%20attack%2C%20Mr%20Saxena%20said%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20health%20department%20had%20recommended%20implementing%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%20in%20June%202018%20and%20the%20then%20health%20minister%20had%20given%20permission%20for%20doing%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20that%2C%20in%20August%202018%2C%20your%20government%20talked%20about%20naming%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%20'Chief%20Minister%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Health%20Insurance%20Scheme%20Ayushman%20Bharat'.%20The%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20which%20bears%20most%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20this%20scheme%2C%20also%20agreed%20to%20your%20self-glorification%20by%20simply%20asking%20you%20to%20use%20your%20name%20after%20'Ayushman%20Bharat'%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lieutenant%20governor%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20scheme%20was%20also%20announced%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly%20in%202020-21%20but%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20%26quot%3Bhunger%20for%20publicity%26quot%3B%20has%20not%20allowed%20it%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Web%20Of%20Illusion'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrongly%20criticising%20the%20Delhi%20health%20model%2C%20Mr%20Saxena%20termed%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bweb%20of%20illusion%26quot%3B%20created%20by%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20%26quot%3Bpropaganda%20machinery%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20been%20suppressing%20the%20CAG%20reports%20of%20the%20health%20department%20for%20years.%20You%20do%20not%20allow%20these%20CAG%20reports%20to%20be%20presented%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20lest%20they%20expose%20your%20web%20of%20illusions.%20Perhaps%20Delhi%20would%20be%20the%20only%20example%20where%20the%20High%20Court%20orders%20the%20health%20minister%20to%20appear%20in%20person%20and%20asks%20him%20to%20make%20medicines%20available%20to%20the%20people.%20Perhaps%20Delhi%20is%20the%20only%20example%20where%20the%20honourable%20courts%20had%20to%20give%20orders%20to%20repair%20the%20CT%20scan%20machine%20in%20the%20biggest%20hospital%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lieutenant%20governor%20also%20accused%20the%20Delhi%20government%20of%20not%20revising%20the%20%26quot%3BEssential%20Drug%20List%26quot%3B%20since%202013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20have%20been%20very%20troubled%20by%20your%20hollow%20health%20model.%20I%20hope%20that%20you%20(Mr%20Kejriwal)%20will%20put%20politics%20aside%2C%20accept%20the%20truth%20and%20implement%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20Since%20you%20are%20no%20longer%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20you%20will%20probably%20not%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20name%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%20after%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Saxena%20sneered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'More%20Procedures%20Covered'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP's%20IT%20Cell%20head%20Amit%20Malviya%20also%20took%20to%20X%20to%20%26quot%3Bexpose%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20lies%20on%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20and%20the%20Delhi%20healthcare%20programme%20and%20said%20that%20while%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20has%20claimed%20that%20there%20is%20no%20upper%20limit%20under%20the%20'Delhi%20Arogya%20Kosh'%2C%20the%20cap%20is%20actually%20Rs%205%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20post%20exposes%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20lies%20on%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20and%20Delhi's%20Healthcare%20Programme.%20Read.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnArvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20been%20refusing%20to%20implement%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Yojana%20in%20Delhi.%20He%20is%20citing%20the%20following%20reasons%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1.%20As%20per%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C