sday%2C%20said%20that%20the%20meeting%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20in%20Russia%20on%20October%2023%20was%20very%20important%20and%20the%20discussions%20between%20them%20will%20serve%20as%20the%20guidelines%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20very%20important%20meeting%20between%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20and%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Now%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20have%20reached%20many%20important%20understandings%2C%20they%20will%20be%20the%20guidelines%20for%20the%20further%20development%20of%20relations%20between%20our%20two%20countries.%20I%20hope%20that%2C%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20this%20consensus%2C%20our%20relations%20will%20be%20moving%20forward%20smoothly%20in%20the%20future%20and%20they%20will%20not%20be%20restricted%20or%20interrupted%20by%20specific%20disagreements%20between%20our%20two%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ambassador%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20some%20differences%20between%20neighbouring%20countries%20are%20natural%2C%20the%20ambassador%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20how%20to%20handle%20and%20solve%20them.%20The%20meeting%20of%20the%20two%20leaders%20has%20set%20a%20very%20good%20example%20for%20us%20on%20how%20to%20handle%20these%20differences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20when%20direct%20flights%20between%20India%20and%20China%20-%20which%20had%20been%20halted%20in%202020%20-%20would%20resume%2C%20the%20ambassador%20elicited%20laughter%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20also%20looking%20forward%20to%20direct%20flights%20so%20I%20can%20fly%20back%20to%20Beijing%20directly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Feihong%20added%20that%20direct%20flights%20would%20be%20convenient%20for%20everybody%20and%20would%20save%20time%20and%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20trade%20ties%2C%20the%20ambassador%20also%20said%20he%20wants%20smooth%20cooperation%20between%20India%20and%20China%20in%20business%2C%20education%2C%20science%20and%20%26quot%3Bevery%20field%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Disengagement%20In%202%20Areas%20Complete'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Feihong's%20comments%20came%20on%20a%20day%20when%20sources%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%20said%20the%20disengagement%20in%20the%20two%20areas%20has%20been%20completed%20and%20patrolling%20would%20begin%20soon.%20The%20modalities%20for%20the%20patrolling%20will%20be%20worked%20out%20by%20ground%20commanders%2C%20the%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20sweets%20would%20be%20exchanged%20with%20Chinese%20troops%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Diwali%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20patrolling%20agreement%20for%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%2C%20which%20had%20been%20announced%20on%20October%2021%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20the%20troops%20would%20return%20to%20the%20positions%20that%20existed%20before%20the%20stand-off%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20began%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20had%20accessed%20satellite%20images%20the%20same%20week%20which%20showed%20that%20structures%20were%20being%20removed%20by%20the%20Chinese%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730296380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fmvn5qm1_modi-xi-jinping_625x300_30_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-china-india-china-agreeement-narendra-modi-important-understandings-reached-chinese-ambassador-on-pm-xi-jinping-meet-6909239%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20week%20after%20India%20announced%20that%20a%20patrolling%20agreement%20had%20been%20reached%20with%20China%20for%20the%20Demchok%20and%20Depsang%20regions%20of%20Eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20Chinese%20ambassador%20to%20the%20country%20has%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bmany%20important%20understandings%26quot%3B%20have%20been%20arrived%20at.%2