ms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fviral-video-shows-how-donald-trump-comes-up-with-his-social-media-posts%2Famp_articleshow%2F114780085.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fviral-video-shows-how-donald-trump-comes-up-with-his-social-media-posts%2Famp_articleshow%2F114780085.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MLA%20Jignesh%20Mevani%20Demands%20IAS%20Officer's%20Suspension%20Over%20'Anti-Dalit'%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGujarat%20Congress%20MLA%20Jignesh%20Mevani%20on%20Wednesday%20demanded%20the%20suspension%20of%20Mahisagar%20District%20Collector%20Neha%20Kumari%2C%20accusing%20her%20of%20making%20anti-Dalit%20comments%2C%20a%20charge%20the%20bureaucrat%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mevani's%20demand%20comes%20a%20week%20after%20he%20sought%20similar%20action%20against%20senior%20IPS%20officer%20Rajkumar%20Pandian%20for%20allegedly%20misbehaving%20with%20him%20and%20one%20of%20his%20party%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLA%20targeted%20Kumari%20citing%20a%20purported%20video%20in%20which%20she%20was%20heard%20saying%20that%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20cases%20registered%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%20or%20the%20Atrocities%20Act%2C%20are%20used%20for%20blackmailing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20termed%20the%20lawmaker's%20claims%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%E2%80%9D%20and%20an%20unsuccessful%20attempt%20to%20get%20political%20mileage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mevani%20visited%20Lunawada%2C%20the%20district%20headquarters%2C%20and%20demanded%20that%20an%20FIR%20be%20registered%20against%20the%20collector%20under%20the%20Atrocities%20Act%20and%20that%20she%20was%20suspended%20over%20her%20%E2%80%9Cinsensitive%E2%80%9D%20remarks%20and%20%E2%80%9Cunparliamentary%E2%80%9D%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20one%20Vijay%20Parmar%20went%20to%20meet%20the%20collector%20with%20his%20grievance%20at%20the%20SWAGAT%20programme%20on%20October%2023%2C%20she%20used%20%E2%80%9Cunparliamentary%E2%80%9D%20words%20against%20him%20and%20also%20insulted%20the%20lawyer%20community%20by%20saying%20they%20should%20be%20%E2%80%9Cslapped%20with%20slippers%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Vadgam%20MLA%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESWAGAT%20is%20an%20initiative%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20for%20the%20redressal%20of%20people's%20grievances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mevani%2C%20the%20collector's%20claim%20that%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20cases%20under%20the%20Atrocities%20Act%20are%20misused%20for%20blackmailing%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20SC%20and%20ST%20communities%20and%20amounts%20to%20an%20offence%20under%20the%20Atrocities%20Act%20and%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20demand%20Kumari's%20suspension%20and%20that%20a%20case%20be%20registered%20against%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20collector%20called%20the%20MLA's%20allegations%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20stunt%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20man%20whom%20the%20MLA%20called%20poor%2C%20innocent%20young%20friend%20(Vijay%20Parmar)%20has%20a%20police%20case%20against%20him%2C%20and%20his%20brother%20has%20more%20than%20one%20case%20of%20rape%2C%20kidnapping%20and%20assault%20against%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumari%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20keep%20visiting%20the%20collector's%20office%20with%20grievances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20SWAGAT%20programme%20on%20October%2023%2C%20he%20pressured%20the%20collector%20to%20file%20a%20case%20against%20police%20officers.%20When%20the%20collector%20told%20him%20that%20she%20did%20not%20have%20the%20power%20to%20file%20a%20case%20and%20that%20he%20should%20approach%20the%20superintendent%20of%20police%20(SP)%20or%20the%20court%2C%20he%20continued%20to%20pester%20her%20over%20his%20issue%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20even%20threatened%20the%20officers%20and%20told%20the%20collector%20that%20she%20was%20a%20Brahmin%20and%20he%20would%20let%20her%20know%20what%20%E2%80%9Csection%204%20of%20the%20Atrocities%20Act%20entailed%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20understand%20the%20direction%20in%20which%20this%20MLA%20wants%20to%20take%20law%20and%20order%20by%20keeping%20a%20person%20with%20a%20criminal%20history%20along%20with%20him%20even%20when%20the%20state%20government%20is%20sensitive%20about%20children%20and%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collector%20said%20that%20the%20way%20Vijay%20Parmar%20is%20%E2%80%9Cblackmailing%E2%80%9D%20government%20employees%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Atrocities%20Act%20is%20not%20at%20all%20right.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20MLA's%20support%20to%20such%20people%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20real%20complainants%20and%20the%20real%20victims%20to%20get%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Congress%20leaders%20and%20Dalit%20community%20members%20gathered%20outside%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Gandhinagar%20demanding%20the%20suspension%20of%20senior%20IPS%20officer%20Rajkumar%20Pandian%20over%20his%20alleged%20misbehaviour%20with%20Mevani%20and%20his%20party%20colleague.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730291400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-mla-jignesh-mevani-demands-ias-officers-suspension-over-anti-dalit-remark-6908487%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gujarat%20Congress%20MLA%20Jignesh%20Mevani%20on%20Wednesday%20demanded%20the%20suspension%20of%20Mahisagar%20District%20Collector%20Neha%20Kumari%2C%20accusing%20her%20o