ity%20Healthcare%20Since%201968%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EL%26amp%3BT%20Health%20Centre%2C%20Andheri%2C%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshok%20Tukaram%20Pawar%20(73)%20is%20eager%20for%20his%20appointment%20slated%20for%20this%20afternoon%20with%20his%20physician%2C%20Padma%20Shri%20awardee%20Dr%20Alaka%20Deshpande.%20It%20is%20a%20weekday%2C%20but%20the%20OPD%20%E2%80%94%20where%20Pawar%20is%20waiting%20with%20the%20other%20patients%2C%20also%20here%20to%20see%20Dr%20Deshpande%20%E2%80%94%20is%20filled%20to%20capacity.%20He%20takes%20advantage%20of%20the%20wait%20to%20explain%20his%20enthusiasm.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20sugar%20levels%20are%20in%20control.%20Doctor%20will%20be%20happy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20ex-L%26amp%3BT%20employee%2C%20Pawar%20learned%20about%20the%20health%20centre%20%E2%80%94%20an%20offshoot%20of%20the%20multinational%E2%80%99s%20CSR%20arm%20%E2%80%94%20during%20his%20tenure%20and%20has%20been%20patronising%20it%20ever%20since.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20told%20my%20neighbours%20and%20friends%20too%2C%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20boasts.%20Once%20under%20the%20impression%20that%20his%20diabetes%20diagnosis%20would%20relegate%20him%20to%20a%20lifetime%20of%20sacrificial%20diets%2C%20Pawar%20says%20he%20found%20hope%20in%20Dr%20Deshpande%E2%80%99s%20fool-proof%20plan%20backed%20by%20promising%20moderate%20lifestyle%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20one%20of%20many%20who%20have%20got%20a%20new%20lease%20on%20life%20through%20these%20holistic%20treatment%20modalities.%20But%2C%20as%20Pawar%20underscores%2C%20access%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20top-notch%20physicians%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20draw%20at%20these%20centres.%20It%20is%20the%20spotlessness%20and%20state-of-the-art%20facilities%20that%20ensure%20a%20steady%20and%20loyal%20patient%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2